MANIFEST

# PyInstaller
#  Usually these files are written by a python script from a template
#  before PyInstaller builds the exe, so you don't need to version them.
#  NOTE: Kiro specs live in .kiro/specs/ and use the .md extension, so they are
#  not affected by this rule.
*.manifest
*.spec

# Installer logs
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

